        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "FIG. 4.— Carnivores (other than hyenas) remains from Fouvent-Saint-Andoche, exclusive of hyenas: A, B, Panthera (Leo) spelaea (Goldfüss, 1810) right upper canines E11.224 (A) and H8.C.241(B); C, Panthera (Leo) spelaea (Goldfüss, 1810) left lower carnassial F10.A.48; D, E, Canis lupus Linnaeus, 1758 right lower carnassial F9.C.264; F, Vulpes vulpesLinnaeus, 1758 left mandible E11.A.15; G, H, Mustela (Putorius) eversmannii left mandible F11.B.214; I, Gulo gulo Linnaeus, 1758 left innominate; J, K, Ursus spelaeus Rosenmüller & Heinroth, 1794 right M2 G9.B.558. Scale bar: 20 mm. Pictures by JBF." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4535133/files/figure.png" .

